Arvind C wrote a review Nov 2018
Hanoi, Vietnam50 contributions24 helpful votes
mesmerising sea view
Sea view rooms on higher floors are just amazing, one can look out to sea for hours. The rooftop swimming pool is a nice add on. Staff is very friendly and breakfast buffet was pretty rich. Stay here if you want to get 100% worth of your money. Do use sun screen the whole time you are at beach or roof top swimming pool, I got sun burned badly in just few hours of exposure.
Read more
Date of stay: November 2018
