Amazing ocean views
We stayed at A La Carte for a short period of time, but it was amazing! The rooftop pool provides a full view of the ocean and parts of the city. Everything from the hotel food, buffet breakfast and staff were great.
Xin chào Ella F, Many thanks for choosing À La Carte and your kind review. We are very happy to hear that everything was alright during your stay and that you appreciated all our services. We hope to welcome you back again soon! Sincerely, The A La Carte management team.
