Kyle Brincefield wrote a review Nov 2018
New York City, New York83 contributions40 helpful votes
Best Hotel on the Beach
Loved every minute of staying at A La Carte Da Nang. The staff was a amazing with a speedy check in and giving us a gorgeous ocean view room on the beach and the morning breakfast was pretty good too. The views from the room balcony and rooftop are incomparable. Wish I could of stayed a week. The rooftop pool is stunning and I would have loved to have more time their as well. I would def recommend and 100% come back. The area is quite nice and we enjoyed watching the locals on the beach in the mornings doing tai chi, meditating, soccer practice and more. Da Nang is a beautiful city, growing at a rapid pace. Get there soon.
