Canterbury, United Kingdom2 contributions4 helpful votes
Great trip to Da Nang
Particularly enjoyed the rooftop infinity pool and bar. Ocean View from our balcony was spectacular - great to wake up to every day. Room was large, well equipped and very clean. Overall a great place to stay in Da Nang. Lavender Bar around the corner was an added extra.
