Karin S wrote a review Oct 2018
173 contributions68 helpful votes
A really good location, next to the beach
Big nice rooms. Some of the has a lovely view over the ocean. This time we got rooms on the side so not so good view. The rooms are clean and fresh. On the top floor there is a very nice pool and when you swim you have the view over the ocean. The service is good. It takes time to get up and down in the elevator. Breakfast is very international and fresh. You have to pay extra for Coffe Latte.
